data.description: This lovely 3bed/1.5 bath is updated and move in ready. Open floor plan to kitchen and living room, featuring stainless steel appliances, and quartz counter tops. The dining room flows off the kitchen, but could be used as a den. Recessed lighting and laminate wood flooring throughout. The roof is a year young. The backyard includes a large shed that could be used as workshop. Buyer to verify measurements during the inspection period.
